        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "2892cd2c-2f95-45a3-8926-683592d96c30",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "医療行為の可否によって、それぞれの業務内容は大きく異なります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "81dfcb77-d676-47df-923e-ea3b67bb4d6b",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "7830229a-8fc2-47a6-bb33-477ddffde4a0",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護師の主な業務"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h3"
      },
      {
        "_key": "21a67b69-9aa4-4a60-bda3-f3e636a6a514",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "c7313d3b-3bf7-46d1-9f21-4d10615749d5",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護師は、専門的な知識と技術に基づき、患者さんの診療や治療に直接関わります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "4d76f301-7250-4e00-abe3-e6e340c032fe",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "cf6d6b3d-db78-4aab-9db9-d1fcb5190652-fbf21563-dea7-443e-bbd2-4f27606a65d7",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "診療の補助"
          },
          {
            "_key": "cf6d6b3d-db78-4aab-9db9-d1fcb5190652-2bc1adcb-7253-43ca-afd4-f4f821117ffc",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": 医師の指示に基づく採血、注射、点滴、与薬など。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "01f70337-4854-4645-9b5e-630504d56f18",
