        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "5c3dd996-8d28-4ece-b863-c9dcdde3b3db-f83c2d80-6843-4a4e-b46b-5b978ea711aa",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "療養上の世話"
          },
          {
            "_key": "5c3dd996-8d28-4ece-b863-c9dcdde3b3db-065fe92d-a241-427d-a8f3-7ee1d75ac054",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": 専門的な知識に基づく健康状態のアセスメント（評価）、ケア計画の立案、褥瘡（床ずれ）の処置など。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "f9736145-647a-4ae4-854d-c4339505263a",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "513ca7bb-2e5e-4f14-a7dd-8eca1218ed99-05ba92d7-203b-4cd9-b29a-7269e852cec1",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "看護計画の立案と評価"
          },
          {
            "_key": "513ca7bb-2e5e-4f14-a7dd-8eca1218ed99-596d2efd-1ab2-4243-937d-3875dbf85460",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": 患者さん一人ひとりの状態に合わせた看護計画を立て、その実施と評価を行います。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "5d4fe7b2-a258-4920-9b48-050b8d1016c0",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "882d7632-5a02-4b34-9b90-b3f02a1a5d20-085fc8b5-31a5-4ec5-b51f-0e8fea80beaf",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "他職種との連携"
          },
          {
            "_key": "882d7632-5a02-4b34-9b90-b3f02a1a5d20-434d17f9-c11e-4b6b-bf3b-12046e84e8ca",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": 医師やリハビリスタッフなど、チーム医療のコーディネート役を担います。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "followup-3fef9674-01fd-48cd-b201-96d48ffb28a4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "text-d4cde9bd-32c8-4182-bab7-b3a5d771df7d",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "上記の点に注意しながら、無理なく取り組んでいきましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "207189d7-c03e-462b-9adc-817f11568d7d",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "32777fe9-48e3-4dbe-ba38-a9b4174a6da6",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護助手の主な業務"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h3"
      },
      {
        "_key": "0705a9f4-5e80-4453-8768-23d8951fbff3",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "541e0760-2af9-482c-add5-feb038226fae",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護助手は、看護師の指示のもと、患者さんの療養生活を支える身の回りのお世話や、環境整備が主な仕事です。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "4966320c-7e55-4cd9-a4f9-6695aa39a6ff",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "3af17753-e6c0-4f07-97a5-539eaf1675d8-290a5980-092a-42a4-9b31-01db6159b94a",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "身体介助"
          },
          {
            "_key": "3af17753-e6c0-4f07-97a5-539eaf1675d8-8d7cbb37-0621-4035-83e9-3666d801a9c4",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": 食事、入浴、排泄の介助、体位変換、移乗の補助など。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "28d4c84c-d8d6-4a57-92e0-804e067fe8f9",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "568df62a-e27f-4de3-8da0-2ea08488e7d4-02e401b2-8b3d-44e0-8715-63ddc406da49",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "環境整備"
          },
          {
            "_key": "568df62a-e27f-4de3-8da0-2ea08488e7d4-ec296b58-b331-4df5-95b6-67869bfa59ef",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": ベッドメイキング、病室の清掃、リネン交換など。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "cba98a56-22d0-4c6f-8521-c61fe89b2b1a",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "a8f3a6b7-eae2-434d-bdf9-6bb3f119e36a-321600e2-e6d4-4c6e-92b3-9eb6ad45ed8a",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "看護師の補助"
          },
          {
            "_key": "a8f3a6b7-eae2-434d-bdf9-6bb3f119e36a-8393b7e1-c6de-4be1-afed-36e186521d06",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": 医療器具の洗浄・準備、メッセンジャー業務、書類整理など。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "section-closing-544fc361-461e-43f4-9a55-4479ec090f1b",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "section-closing-span-eee6017f-a912-4a25-aaf2-d67fcd516f54",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "業務内容の違いでは、看護師と連携しながら無理のない範囲で進めることが大切です。気になる点はその都度共有し、安全第一で取り組みましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "06fc2527-09f7-40d7-ab8d-fff48e2993b4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "dd229659-e4ea-4315-8f03-0323114e9689",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "役割と責任の違い"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "f4ef67d0-5c94-4280-bca4-651afb3db6fe",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "023ff63e-9009-429a-87c7-5cee00048add-0124444e-b660-4d9c-9202-2baa34cfc1ef",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "看護師"
          },
          {
            "_key": "023ff63e-9009-429a-87c7-5cee00048add-0c864641-f3b7-4e04-b76d-232e7be02a03",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": 患者さんの健康状態や生命に直接関わる医療行為を行うため、その判断と実施に対して重大な責任を負います。看護助手が安全に業務を行えるよう、適切に指示を出し、監督する責任もあります。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "9299c328-bef9-472e-9b8d-c5985b37379a",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "674c34a6-c8e1-4d71-a1c0-0f0b763cda86-6be56194-ab9d-4723-bc95-fca1def6421a",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "看護助手"
          },
          {
            "_key": "674c34a6-c8e1-4d71-a1c0-0f0b763cda86-9d591b4f-9f58-4f23-a39c-fcbbe6bee3a4",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": 看護師の指示を正確に実行する責任があります。患者さんの状態に異変を感じた際は、自己判断せずに速やかに看護師に報告する義務があります。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "section-closing-660847b0-ac6f-4fd6-ba90-eef45bb38698",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "section-closing-span-7db02144-c344-407f-943d-cd62fd45c3cc",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "役割と責任の違いでは、看護師と連携しながら無理のない範囲で進めることが大切です。気になる点はその都度共有し、安全第一で取り組みましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
